Create a CSS skew transformation of 30 degrees on a table consisting of multiple rows and columns, effectively changing their shape. The table in question is as follows:
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;Data 1&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;Data 2&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;Data 3&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;Data 4&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
